int EVL_CFG_T::psfol

compute Open loop PSF.

  • 1: on axis only.
  • 2: all directions and average them.

int EVL_CFG_T::rmax

max radial mode for performance evaluation.

  • 0: piston only
  • 1: piston/tip/tilt.

int EVL_CFG_T::nmod

Number of modes.

derived from rmax. (nmax+1)*(nmax+2)/2

int EVL_CFG_T::psfisim

time step to start psfmean.

int EVL_CFG_T::psfsize

FFT size for outputing PSF.

Becareful about FFT speed and enough padding. Determines the sampling of the generated PSF

int* EVL_CFG_T::psfgridsize

grid size for FFT to generate PSF.

Becareful about FFT speed and enough padding. Determines the sampling of the generated PSF. 0 or negative for automatic.
